oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Update on Prostaglandin
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Mickelsen, W. Duane
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: prostaglandins
veterinary use
estrus synchronization
fertility work
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Much has been said and written about prostaglandins in the past few years. Two products are now commercially available for veterinary use in mares. The efficacy of prostaglandins has been well established in cattle for estrus synchronization and now therapeutic use, especially in dairy fertility work, but as yet they are not available commercially.
